  $( A commutative ring is a ring.  (Contributed by Jeff Madsen,
     10-Jun-2010.) $)
  crngrng $p |- ( R e. CRing -> R e. RingOps ) $=
    ( ccring wcel cring ccm2 iscring simplbi ) ABCADCAECAFG $.
    $( [10-Jun-2010] $)

  ${
    $d X x y $.  $d A x y $.  $d B y $.  $d H x y $.  $d R x y $.
    crngcom.1 $e |- G = ( 1st ` R ) $.
    crngcom.2 $e |- H = ( 2nd ` R ) $.
    crngcom.3 $e |- X = ran G $.
    $( The multiplication operation of a commutative ring is commutative.
       (Contributed by Jeff Madsen, 8-Jun-2010.) $)
    crngcom $p |- ( ( R e. CRing /\ A e. X /\ B e. X )
                                        -> ( A H B ) = ( B H A ) ) $=
      ( vx vy ccring wcel co wceq cv wral wa cring iscring2 simprbi opreq1
      opreq2 eqeq12d rcla42v mpan9 3impb ) CLMZAFMZBFMZABENZBAENZOZUHJPZKPZENZU
      OUNENZOZKFQJFQZUIUJRUMUHCSMUSJKCDEFGHITUAURUMAUOENZUOAENZOJKABFFUNAOUPUTU
      QVAUNAUOEUBUNAUOEUCUDUOBOUTUKVAULUOBAEUCUOBAEUBUDUEUFUG $.
      $( [8-Jun-2010] $)
  $}

  ${
    crngm.1 $e |- G = ( 1st ` R ) $.
    crngm.2 $e |- H = ( 2nd ` R ) $.
    crngm.3 $e |- X = ran G $.
    $( Commutative/associative law for commutative rings.  (Contributed by Jeff
       Madsen, 19-Jun-2010.) $)
    crngm23 $p |- ( ( R e. CRing /\ ( A e. X /\ B e. X /\ C e. X ) )
                                -> ( ( A H B ) H C ) = ( ( A H C ) H B ) ) $=
      ( ccring wcel w3a wa co wceq crngcom 3adant3r1 opreq2d cring crngrng
      ringoass sylan 3exp2 com34 3imp2 3eqtr4d ) DKLZAGLZBGLZCGLZMZNZABCFOZFOZA
